<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SQ1 Campus Assessment Portal</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f9fafb;
        color: #1f2937;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo img {
        width: 100px;
        height: auto;
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #fd0076;
      }
      h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #374151;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      ul {
        margin: 15px 0 20px 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: block;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 30px auto 0;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fd0076, #3b82f6);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background: #fd0076;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .highlight {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #fd0076;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="SQ1 Logo" />
      </div>
 
      <h1>Welcome To The SQ1 Campus Assessment Portal</h1>
      <h2>Preparing For a Seamless Campus Hiring Experience</h2>
 
      <p>
        Thank you for partnering with <span class="highlight">SQ1</span> for
        your upcoming campus assessment process. This secure assessment portal
        is designed to ensure a smooth and efficient experience for your
        students and placement team.
      </p>
 
      <p>Please use this page to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Verify Portal Access:</strong> Confirm that your network
          allows access the platform before getting into the assessment.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Support Contact:</strong> If you face any issues accessing
          this page or encounter errors, contact our technical support
          immediately so we can resolve problems before the event.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Data Security Notice:</strong> This portal and all assessments
          are secured by SQ1â€™s next-gen cybersecurity systems. All candidate's
          data and submissions are protected under industry best practices.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Assessment Day Preparation:</strong> On the assessment day,
          you will receive a unique link. Please ensure students can log in and
          have read instructions provided.
        </li>
      </ul>
 
      <p>
        We look forward to helping your students succeed and ensuring a flawless
        campus hiring process!
      </p>
 
      <p>
        <strong>For questions or support, please contact:</strong><br />
        Email:
        <a href="mailto:support@sq1security.com" class="highlight"
          >hr.talentacquisition@sq1.security</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
 
 